headline: AI employment in major banks sees 13% rise, reports Evident
summary: A recent report from Evident, a platform focused on AI benchmarking, has revealed a 13% rise in AI employment among major global banks. This increase in AI personnel has occurred over two years, despite ongoing market fluctuations. The analysis shows that currently, one in every 50 banking employees holds a role specifically related to AI.…
